le=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">s</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">w</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">d</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">l</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">i</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">v</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">r</span></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Results we deliver</span></h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-[#A1A1AA] text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl\">Real projects. Real outcomes. Each engagement is tailored to the specific operations and goals of the business.</p></div><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div string=\"magnetic\" string-radius=\"600\" string-strength=\"0.08\" class=\"group relative bg-[#111111] rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col hover:bg-[#161616] transition-colors duration-500 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586528116311-ad8dd3c8310d?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=center\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#111111] via-[#111111]/60 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-start justify-between mb-6\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider\">Logistics</p><h3 class=\"mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white\">LogiChain Solutions</h3></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right w-4 h-4 text-[#52525B] mt-1 shrink-0 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-4 flex-1 relative z-10\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Challenge</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Manual order processing across 3 systems required 40+ hours of data entry per week, with frequent errors.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Solution</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Deployed an AI agent that reads incoming orders from email, validates inventory, creates records in their ERP, and updates the CRM.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#27272A] relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span>%</span></div><div class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] mt-0.5\">Manual work eliminated</div></div></div><div string=\"magnetic\" string-radius=\"600\" string-strength=\"0.08\" class=\"group relative bg-[#111111] rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col hover:bg-[#161616] transition-colors duration-500 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160399-112ba8d25d1d?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=center\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#111111] via-[#111111]/60 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-start justify-between mb-6\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider\">Healthcare</p><h3 class=\"mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white\">MediConnect Health</h3></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right w-4 h-4 text-[#52525B] mt-1 shrink-0 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-4 flex-1 relative z-10\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Challenge</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Patient support team was overwhelmed with 500+ daily inquiries, average response time of 8 hours.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Solution</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Built a RAG-powered AI chatbot trained on clinical protocols, insurance policies, and FAQs, integrated with WhatsApp.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#27272A] relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span>s</span></div><div class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] mt-0.5\">Average response time</div></div></div><div string=\"magnetic\" string-radius=\"600\" string-strength=\"0.08\" class=\"group relative bg-[#111111] rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col hover:bg-[#161616] transition-colors duration-500 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564013799919-ab600027ffc6?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=center\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#111111] via-[#111111]/60 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-start justify-between mb-6\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider\">Real Estate</p><h3 class=\"mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Prime Realty Group</h3></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right w-4 h-4 text-[#52525B] mt-1 shrink-0 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-4 flex-1 relative z-10\"><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Challenge</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Sales team manually entering lead data from Zillow, Realtor.com, and their website into Salesforce.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Solution</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Developed an automated lead ingestion pipeline with AI enrichment that scores and routes leads to the right agent.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#27272A] relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent\"><span class=\"\"><span>0</span>s</span></div><div class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] mt-0.5\">Lead response time</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-padding bg-[#090909] relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-shape section-shape-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"section-shape section-shape-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"container-app relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mb-16 sm:mb-20\"><h2 class=\"heading-lg text-white\" style=\"cursor:default\"><style>\n        @font-face {\n          font-family: 'InterVariable';\n          src: url('https://rsms.me/inter/font-files/InterVariable.woff2?v=4.0') format('woff2-variations');\n          font-weight: 100 900;\n          font-style: normal;\n          font-display: swap;\n        }\n      </style><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">B</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">u</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">i</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">l</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">t</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">d</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">i</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">f</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">f</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">r</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">n</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">t</span></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Built different</span></h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-[#A1A1AA] text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl\">We combine deep technical expertise with a practical understanding of how businesses actually operate. Here&#x27;s why clients trust us.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 auto-rows-[minmax(180px,auto)]\"><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-1 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/[0.06] via-transparent to-accent/[0.02]\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><path d=\"M6 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18Z\"></path><path d=\"M6 12H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2\"></path><path d=\"M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M10 6h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 10h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 14h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 18h4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">01</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Business-first approach</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Every solution starts with understanding your operations and goals. Outcomes, not technology.</p></div></div><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-2 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-accent/[0.03] to-transparent rounded-bl-full\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"></path><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">02</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Fast deployment</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Most projects move from kickoff to production in under 4 weeks.</p></div></div><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-1 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]\"><div class=\"w-full h-full\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" x=\"4\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"6\" height=\"6\" x=\"9\" y=\"9\" rx=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M15 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M15 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 20v2\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">03</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Modern AI stack</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">The latest models — OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, open-source, and custom fine-tuned models.</p></div></div><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-1 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-[0.04]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-around\"><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:63%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:100%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:86%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:72%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:58%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:95%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:81%\"></div><div class=\"h-px bg-white\" style=\"width:67%\"></div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-git-branch w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"15\"></line><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"6\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M18 9a9 9 0 0 1-9 9\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">04</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Scalable architecture</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Built to grow with you. Systems that handle increasing volume without degradation.</p></div></div><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-1 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/[0.06] via-transparent to-emerald-500/[0.02]\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">05</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Enterprise security</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Data privacy and security baked into every layer. SOC 2 principles guide our architecture.</p></div></div><div class=\"bento-cell group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-6 sm:p-8 lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-1 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616]\" style=\"min-height:180px\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]\"><div class=\"w-full h-full\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:16px 16px\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-auto\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-accent/40 transition-colors duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones w-[18px] h-[18px] text-accent\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[#3F3F46] group-hover:text-[#52525B] transition-colors duration-300\">06</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Dedicated support</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-xs text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Every client gets a direct line to their project team. No account managers, no runaround.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#090909] overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"section-shape section-shape-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"section-shape section-shape-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.015]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px\"></div><style>\n        @keyframes ping {\n          0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); }\n          50% { opacity: 1; }\n          100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(1.5); }\n        }\n        @keyframes wave {\n          0% { transform: scaleY(0.5); }\n          100% { transform: scaleY(1.2); }\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse-dot {\n          0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); }\n          50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.8); }\n        }\n        @keyframes rise {\n          0% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 0; }\n          20% { opacity: 1; }\n          100% { transform: translateY(-400px) scale(0.3); opacity: 0; }\n        }\n        @keyframes spin {\n          0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n          100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n        }\n      </style><div class=\"container-app pt-20 sm:pt-24 lg:pt-32\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mb-14 sm:mb-20\"><h2 class=\"heading-lg text-white\" style=\"cursor:default\"><style>\n        @font-face {\n          font-family: 'InterVariable';\n          src: url('https://rsms.me/inter/font-files/InterVariable.woff2?v=4.0') format('woff2-variations');\n          font-weight: 100 900;\n          font-style: normal;\n          font-display: swap;\n        }\n      </style><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">H</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">o</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">w</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">w</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">w</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">o</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">r</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">k</span></span><span class=\"sr-only\">How we work</span></h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-[#A1A1AA] text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl\">A structured but flexible approach that keeps projects moving without sacrificing quality.</p></div></div><div class=\"container-app pb-24 sm:pb-32 lg:pb-40\"><div class=\"space-y-12 sm:space-y-16\"><div class=\"process-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(39,39,42,1);background-color:#111111;transition:border-color 0.5s, background-color 0.5s\"><div class=\"absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-56 h-56 rounded-full pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, hsla(250, 60%, 60%, 0.12), transparent 70%);filter:blur(60px)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute rounded-full border opacity-[0.06]\" style=\"left:20%;top:50%;width:200px;hei