ld leading-none mb-4 select-none\" style=\"color:hsla(160, 55%, 50%, 0.1)\">02</div><div class=\"card-icon w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-3\" style=\"background-color:hsla(160, 55%, 50%, 0.1);border:1px solid hsla(160, 55%, 50%, 0.2)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-line w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:hsl(160, 55%, 50%)\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"card-title text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">Strategy</h3><p class=\"card-desc text-[#A1A1AA] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">A detailed roadmap with architecture decisions, timeline, metrics, and expected ROI.</p><p class=\"card-detail text-sm text-[#71717A] leading-relaxed max-w-xl mt-2\">Technology selection, proof of concept, sprint planning, and success criteria definition.</p></div></div><div class=\"process-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(39,39,42,1);background-color:#111111;transition:border-color 0.5s, background-color 0.5s\"><div class=\"absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-56 h-56 rounded-full pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, hsla(270, 60%, 60%, 0.12), transparent 70%);filter:blur(60px)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-[0.05]\"><div class=\"w-full h-full\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px),\n            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px\"></div><div class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"left:20%;top:30%;width:6px;height:6px;background-color:hsl(270, 70%, 60%);box-shadow:0 0 12px hsla(270, 70%, 60%, 0.4);animation:pulse-dot 2s 0s ease-in-out infinite\"></div><div class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"left:42%;top:65%;width:6px;height:6px;background-color:hsl(270, 70%, 60%);box-shadow:0 0 12px hsla(270, 70%, 60%, 0.4);animation:pulse-dot 2s 0.4s ease-in-out infinite\"></div><div class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"left:64%;top:30%;width:6px;height:6px;background-color:hsl(270, 70%, 60%);box-shadow:0 0 12px hsla(270, 70%, 60%, 0.4);animation:pulse-dot 2s 0.8s ease-in-out infinite\"></div><div class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"left:86%;top:65%;width:6px;height:6px;background-color:hsl(270, 70%, 60%);box-shadow:0 0 12px hsla(270, 70%, 60%, 0.4);animation:pulse-dot 2s 1.2000000000000002s ease-in-out infinite\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10\"><div class=\"card-number inline-block text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-none mb-4 select-none\" style=\"color:hsla(270, 55%, 50%, 0.1)\">03</div><div class=\"card-icon w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-3\" style=\"background-color:hsla(270, 55%, 50%, 0.1);border:1px solid hsla(270, 55%, 50%, 0.2)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code-xml w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:hsl(270, 55%, 50%)\"><path d=\"m18 16 4-4-4-4\"></path><path d=\"m6 8-4 4 4 4\"></path><path d=\"m14.5 4-5 16\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"card-title text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">Development</h3><p class=\"card-desc text-[#A1A1AA] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">Agile sprints. You see progress weekly. No black boxes, no surprises.</p><p class=\"card-detail text-sm text-[#71717A] leading-relaxed max-w-xl mt-2\">Iterative builds with continuous integration, automated testing, and weekly demo reviews.</p></div></div><div class=\"process-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\" style=\"borde