.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-1.982.553-3.866 1.583-4.95C5.411 6.988 6.684 6.25 8 6.25V9.5c-.975.25-1.679.832-2 2.25h2v6H4.583zM14.583 17.321C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-1.982.553-3.866 1.583-4.95C15.411 6.988 16.684 6.25 18 6.25V9.5c-.975.25-1.679.832-2 2.25h2v6h-3.417z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"flex-1 text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">“<!-- -->The workflow automation they designed saved us over 40 hours a week across our logistics operations. The ROI was obvious within the first month.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#27272A]\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-white\">Rachel Torres</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] mt-0.5\">VP Operations, LogiChain Solutions</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-accent/20 mb-6\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M4.583 17.321C3.553 16.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-1.982.553-3.866 1.583-4.95C5.411 6.988 6.684 6.25 8 6.25V9.5c-.975.25-1.679.832-2 2.25h2v6H4.583zM14.583 17.321C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-1.982.553-3.866 1.583-4.95C15.411 6.988 16.684 6.25 18 6.25V9.5c-.975.25-1.679.832-2 2.25h2v6h-3.417z\"></path></svg><blockquote class=\"flex-1 text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">“<!-- -->We were skeptical about AI until we saw the lead response system Sericaway built. Our conversion rate increased by 35% in the first quarter.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[#27272A]\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-white\">Marcus Chen</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] mt-0.5\">CEO, Prime Realty Group</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"section-padding bg-[#090909] overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"section-shape section-shape-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"container-app mb-16 sm:mb-20\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4\">About</p><h2 class=\"heading-lg text-white\" style=\"cursor:default\"><style>\n        @font-face {\n          font-family: 'InterVariable';\n          src: url('https://rsms.me/inter/font-files/InterVariable.woff2?v=4.0') format('woff2-variations');\n          font-weight: 100 900;\n          font-style: normal;\n          font-display: swap;\n        }\n      </style><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">W</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">h</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">o</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">w</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\"> </span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">a</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">r</span><span class=\"wh-letter\" style=\"display:inline-block;white-space:pre;font-family:&quot;InterVariable&quot;, &quot;Inter&quot;, system-ui, sans-serif;font-variation-settings:&#x27;wght&#x27; 400\">e</span></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Who we are</span></h2></div><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><p class=\"text-[#A1A1AA] text-base leading-relaxed\">Sericaway was founded on a simple idea: AI should make business easier, not more complicated. We combine deep technical expertise with practical business understanding to build systems that deliver measurable results.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-6\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-white\">Vaibhav Tayade</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] mt-0.5\">Founder</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-white\">Yugandhar Pise</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#52525B] mt-0.5\">Founder</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container-app\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"about-card rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-8 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616] transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-6 h-6 text-accent\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Our Mission</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">We help businesses eliminate repetitive work through AI agents, workflow automation, and intelligent software — freeing teams to focus on what matters.</p></div><div class=\"about-card rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-8 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616] transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye w-6 h-6 text-accent\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Our Vision</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">A world where every business, regardless of size, can leverage AI to operate more efficiently, compete with larger players, and grow without limits.</p></div><div class=\"about-card rounded-2xl border border-[#27272A] bg-[#111111] p-8 hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-[#161616] transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-6 h-6 text-accent\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Our Values</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed\">Transparency, craftsmanship, and results. We communicate honestly, b